{"tid":1014131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小兄弟濕地公園忽失蹤　弟弟遺體40小時後河中尋回","createTime":"2019-02-09T02:45:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T10:55:08.000Z","uid":54337,"like":170,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"606d5f1e51f823a6c790820224e914fe4217acff","tid":1014131,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T02:45:20.000Z","msg":"小兄弟濕地公園忽失蹤　弟弟遺體40小時後河中尋回<br />\n<br />\n江西鷹潭市15歲男童夏瑞廷，周三（6日）下午帶同10歲弟弟夏豪廷離開外婆家，外出玩耍時，在鷹潭濕地公園附近失蹤。家人其後報警求助，警員及救援隊搜索40多個小時後，在公園對面的小河中尋回夏豪廷的屍體，惟哥哥仍然失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳消息指，警方已就事件立案調查，初步懷疑兄弟兩人曾被「拐子佬」拐走；惟警方未有證實有關消息真偽，僅確認已尋回一具男童遺體，另一名男童則仍在搜救當中；對於事件是否有刑事成分，仍待警方後續調查確認。"},{"pid":"7620d824c40dced55cadc44b3f6a08e115bce47b","tid":1014131,"uid":54337,"like":258,"dislike":10,"score":248,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T02:45:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">牠只是孩子呀</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b6caa971631c414547d9d803e52601128002ea7a","tid":1014131,"uid":54337,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T02:46:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190209/photo/bkn-20190209073312206-0209_00952_001_02p.jpg?20190209074938\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190209%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190209073312206-0209_00952_001_02p.jpg%3F20190209074938&h=d04215a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"715470daa7aee853da172091b07cb564c9aeb64a","tid":1014131,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T02:46:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190209/mobile/bkn-20190209073312206-0209_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190209%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190209073312206-0209_00952_001.html&d=6BLFUKkZTytPAocRz50jI9qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=298cf073\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190209/mobile/bkn-201902